Hey, Ryan. Come on. Come on up.

01:26:55.908 --> 01:26:59.857
You okay? Here. Here.

01:27:07.127 --> 01:27:08.821
His name's Alex.

01:27:08.921 --> 01:27:12.740
I want you to look after
him as if he were your own.

01:27:16.512 --> 01:27:18.622
Thank you so much.

