all hang until we figure things out.

01:31:06.950 --> 01:31:08.480
Mmm.

01:31:11.872 --> 01:31:16.569
Baby, that was no minor surgery.
You need to rest.

01:31:20.923 --> 01:31:22.998
I have an idea.

01:31:29.723 --> 01:31:31.882
You take control.

